Ing '''M4 carbine''' metung yang familiang baril nung nu abaligdan me ing kayang penibatan kareng mumunang [[carbine]] versions na ning [[M16 rifle|M16]], iti menibat la keng orihinal [[AR-15]] a gawa ning [[ArmaLite]]. Iti malati ya at mayan yang uangis kesa keng [[M16 rifle#M16A2|M16A2]] [[assault rifle]], a atin kalupang 80% dake na ning  M16A2.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.specialoperations.com/Weapons/Features/M4/Page_Two.htm |title=The Design & Development of the M-4 Carbine |publisher=Special Operations.Com |accessdate=2008-11-08}}</ref> Ing '''M4''' atin yang [[pipamilinan akbung]] kayabe ne ing [[Semi-automatic firearm|semi-automatic]] ampong [[Burst mode (firearm)|atlung-durut a lapitpit]] (kalupa ning M16A2), kabang ing '''M4A1''' atin yang "[[Automatic firearm|full auto]]" a pipimilinan imbes na ing atlung-durut a lapitpit.


